Author: ISBbaby
Text: A counselor or therapist doesn't pursue that for a paycheck, that's for sure. They do it specifically because they care.   You deserve health and success, and you need to do what you need to do in order to stabilize and become healthy, not just for yourself, but also for your family who loves you and wants to see you doing well.
